<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nero — Porto</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --bg: #060810;
    --bg2: #090c14;
    --surface: #0d1220;
    --border: rgba(60,100,200,0.12);
    --text: #d6dff5;
    --muted: #4a5878;
    --accent: #4f8ef7;
    --accent2: #1a3a7a;
    --accent-dark: #1e2d52;
    --glow: rgba(79,142,247,0.12);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    cursor: crosshair;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* grain overlay */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 999;
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 2px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--accent2); }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.4s, background 0.4s;
  }
  nav.scrolled {
    background: rgba(6,8,16,0.92);
    border-color: var(--border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 3rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 50% at 65% 35%, rgba(30,60,140,0.18) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 35% 50% at 15% 75%, rgba(10,30,90,0.12) 0%, transparent 55%);
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 11rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.5s forwards;
  }
  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 420px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.8s forwards;
  }

  .hero-line {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3rem;
    right: 3rem;
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s 1.2s forwards;
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section {
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* PHOTO PLACEHOLDER */
  .photo-wrap {
    width: 200px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 200px;
    height: 260px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .photo-placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,142,247,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  /* corner decorations */
  .photo-placeholder::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px; left: 8px; right: 8px; bottom: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,142,247,0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .photo-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--accent-dark);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .photo-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; stroke: var(--accent); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; stroke-linecap: round; }
  .photo-placeholder-text {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .photo-caption {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .about-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2.5rem; }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .about-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .stat {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-desc {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* SKILLS */
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .skill-card {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .skill-card:hover { background: var(--surface); }
  .skill-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 2px;
    height: 0;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: height 0.4s ease;
  }
  .skill-card:hover::before { height: 100%; }
  .skill-icon {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .skill-name {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .skill-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .skill-level {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .skill-level::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }
  .skill-card[data-level="pro"] .skill-level::after { width: 75%; }
  .skill-card[data-level="mid"] .skill-level::after { width: 40%; }

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .contact-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contact-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .contact-text p { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 1rem; }
  .contact-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .contact-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: padding-left 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .contact-link:hover { padding-left: 0.8rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .contact-link span {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .hero { padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; }
    section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .photo-wrap { width: 100%; }
    .photo-placeholder { width: 100%; height: 220px; }
    .about-stats { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">NERO</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Tentang</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Kontak</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-label">Portfolio — 2026</div>
  <h1 class="hero-name"><em>Nero</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Seorang penyendiri yang lebih nyaman berbicara lewat gambar dan teks.</p>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-label">01 — Siapa saya</div>
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="photo-wrap">
      <div class="photo-placeholder">
        <div class="photo-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-placeholder-text">Foto kamu<br>di sini</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-caption">[ ganti dengan foto asli ]</div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-right">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Anak yang <em>lebih suka diam,</em> tapi punya banyak cerita.</h2>
        <p>Halo. Nama saya Nero. Saya bukan tipe yang mudah membuka diri — tapi di balik keheningan itu, ada seseorang yang mengamati dunia dengan seksama, menciptakan sesuatu dari apa yang dilihat.</p>
        <p>Saya percaya bahwa introvert bukan berarti tidak punya suara. Saya berbicara lewat foto dan kode.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Jam mengamati dunia</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">2</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Bidang yang digeluti</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">0</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Urgensi tampil ramai</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section id="skills">
  <div class="section-label">02 — Apa yang saya lakukan</div>
  <div class="skills-grid reveal">
    <div class="skill-card" data-level="pro">
      <div class="skill-icon">01 / FOTOGRAFER</div>
      <div class="skill-name">Photography</div>
      <div class="skill-desc">Melihat momen yang orang lain lewatkan. Komposisi, cahaya, dan kesunyian.</div>
      <div class="skill-level"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-card" data-level="mid">
      <div class="skill-icon">02 / CODING</div>
      <div class="skill-name">Development</div>
      <div class="skill-desc">Masih belajar, tapi tekun. Kode adalah bahasa lain untuk menceritakan sesuatu.</div>
      <div class="skill-level"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="section-label">03 — Temukan saya</div>
  <div class="contact-inner reveal">
    <div class="contact-text">
      <h2>Mari <em>terhubung,</em> kalau kamu tidak keberatan dengan keheningan.</h2>
      <p>Saya tidak terlalu sering online, tapi pesan kamu pasti terbaca — suatu saat.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a href="#" class="contact-link">Instagram <span>@nero</span></a>
      <a href="#" class="contact-link">Twitter / X <span>@nero</span></a>
      <a href="mailto:nero@email.com" class="contact-link">Email <span>nero@email.com</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <span>© 2024 Nero</span>
  <span>The Antisocial Archive</span>
  <span>Made with silence.</span>
</footer>

<script>
  const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 60);
  });

  const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(e => {
      if (e.isIntersecting) {
        e.target.classList.add('visible');
        observer.unobserve(e.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.12 });
  reveals.forEach(r => observer.observe(r));
</script>
</body>
</html>